{"tid":773182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律師費料花220萬元","createTime":"2018-08-09T10:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T10:59:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"754d2b06320a401a3f4b16c92c4c69cf2d8819b4","tid":773182,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:18:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180809/20472139\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180809%2F20472139&d=4HARd12Fs2HlhsTp1kULoU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=bc16add0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180809%2F20472139&h=2b4687d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180809/20472139</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年08月09日 <br />\n<br />\n律師費料花220萬元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180809/large/a0503a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180809%2Flarge%2Fa0503a.gif&h=eb5e5c5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】朱經緯身為警司，退休生活理應相當富裕。有報道指朱不但每月領取5萬元長俸，亦已收取一筆過逾300萬元退休金。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資深大狀擅刑事案<br />\n<br />\n今次上訴，朱請來知名資深大律師郭莎樂（Charlotte Draycott）上陣，連同原審時為他辯護的大律師彭彼得（Peter Pannu），有律師估計上訴律師費達150萬元，加上原審時的律師費，朱埋單要220萬元，令積蓄大縮水。<br />\n<br />\n郭莎樂1988年在本港成為大律師，擅打刑事案。有律師估計，她與彭彼得兩天收費共100萬元，當中郭佔65萬元，加上事務律師費用，上訴要花150萬元。而早前原審時開庭10天，估計彭連事務律師共收70萬元。<br />\n<br />\n郭莎樂曾為轟動全城的大角嘴碎屍案其中一名被告謝臻麒辯護，最終謝謀殺罪脫，當庭釋放。近期她亦為七警之一的關嘉豪申請保釋外出等候上訴。<br />\n<br />\n至於大律師彭彼得曾任職反黑組高級督察，曾涉嫌收賄及傷人脫罪，後來轉戰法律界，1997年成為大律師。他與因洗黑錢入獄的商人楊家誠是好友，曾出任伯明翰環球行政總裁，後被撤職。<br />\n<br />\n■記者蘇曉欣  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n稱事主證供存28疑點<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n藝人余德丞踢波昏迷入ICU<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱事主證供存28疑點<br />\n<br />\n朱經緯上訴　申蘋果動新聞片呈堂指顯示被毆者停留罵警非路過"},{"pid":"35203843000b7d5c1258bcef4b38d295fc53f2dd","tid":773182,"uid":8439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:22:24.000Z","msg":"話曬大家都係黑警 收順d得唔得"},{"pid":"9b38655734b55629cc92c4347a9a894532e5ac39","tid":773182,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:51:01.000Z","msg":"啲同袍幫佢籌旗使撚自己俾咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e71fd8728ae6da5255385628995fb6d72fa800a","tid":773182,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:52:05.000Z","msg":"大把愛國團體幫佢俾啦,佢駛撚出錢咩"},{"pid":"771b7e6939b04faec484816edea67628828f3bcd","tid":773182,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:53:03.000Z","msg":"施君龍殺人放火都咁富貴啦過得<br />\n佢點會無錢呀"},{"pid":"79d8096f8bfbde48f8a3a3e59de18bdc95691dd3","tid":773182,"uid":33352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:55:17.000Z","msg":"包攬訴訟有無得查"},{"pid":"24769b91201edc1b7888702a9c245f11a33520de","tid":773182,"uid":101895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:57:16.000Z","msg":"呢隻白皮豬真係咁把炮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"580e9d0035856e13dd774661af606b2c978d0af3","tid":773182,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T10:59:28.000Z","msg":"律師果然係為有錢人發聲"}]}